727611f-b.title: Queens: Northern Boulevard - Junction Boulevard
727611f-b.text:
Northern Boulevard, north side, from Junction Boulevard
to 95th Street, showing Pfistner's roadhouse, built on the
site of J. Carroll's roadhouse. This place was gone in 1928.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection  Views 1,2: March, 1924
MAY BE REPRODUCED  View 3: Oct., 1925
